            <!-- dont let profile-card grow upwards as it gets longer in text-->
            <p>
            <h2>
                The Spear of Vengence
            </h2>
            <!--align the text to the left-->
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 100;" class="story">
                <!-- <b style="font-size: large;">LORE: </b> -->
                An undying specter of wrath and retribution, Kalista is an armored nightmare summoned from the Shadow Isles to hunt deceivers and traitors. 
                The betrayed may cry out in blood to be avenged, but Kalista only answers those willing to pay with their very souls. 
                Those who become the focus of Kalista’s wrath should make their final peace, for any pact sealed with this grim hunter can only be ended by 
                the cold, piercing fire of her soul-spears.
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin-top: 8%; text-align: center; font-size: 25px;filter:drop-shadow(5);" id="buildStory">
                Build your story!
            </h3>
            <!-- insert a text box and a button that says make your story-->
            <input class="inputBox" type="text" name="story" placeholder="What is your name?" style="margin-top: 5%;"
                required="required" id="inputHider">
            <a class="button1" font-size="25" id="disableMe">Away we go!</a>
            <!-- disable button1 after it is clicked-->

            <!-- make an api call when the button is pressed, use the input as query for the api call-->
            <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.0.min.js"></script>
            <script>
                // make an api call when the button is pressed, use the input as query for the api call
                $(".button1").click(function () {
                    const btn = document.getElementById('disableMe');
                    btn.style.display = 'none';
                    const input = document.getElementById('inputHider');
                    input.style.display = 'none';
                    const story = document.getElementById('buildStory');
                    story.style.display = 'none';
                    var name = $(".inputBox").val();
                    console.log(name);
                    if (name.length = 0 || name === undefined || name === null || name === "") {
                        alert("Please enter a name");
                    } else {
                        console.log(name);
                        $(".story").append('<br><br>');
                        var i = 0;
                        var txt = `${name} had always been a bit of a loner. He was never really one for socializing, preferring to spend his time on his own. But that all changed when he met Kalista.

Kalista was everything that ${name} was not. She was outgoing and vivacious, always looking for a good time. She was also incredibly brave, never afraid to stand up for what she believed in.

${name} was immediately drawn to Kalista, and the two of them quickly became close friends. They would spend hours talking, and ${name} found himself opening up to her in ways he never had before.

Then, one day, everything changed. ${name} learned that Kalista had been betrayed by someone she trusted. He was furious, and vowed to help her get revenge.

Kalista was hesitant at first, but eventually she agreed. Together, they plotted and planned, until the day came to take their revenge.

${name} will never forget that day. It was the day he finally stood up for himself, and for Kalista. It was the day he became a soul-spear, and ended the betrayer's reign`; /* The text */
                        var speed = 1; /* The speed/duration of the effect in milliseconds */
                        // make the color of the text change
                        function typeWriter() {
                            if (i < txt.length) {
                                // make the color of the text change
                                $(".story").append(txt.charAt(i));
                                i++;
                                setTimeout(typeWriter, speed);
                            }
                        }
                        function endingText() {
                            $(".story").append('<br><br>');
                            $(".story").append('<b>This story was generated with GPT3!</b>');
                        }
                        function endingTextTwo() {
                            $(".story").append('<br><br><br>');
                            $(".story").append('<a class="button1" font-size="25" id="enableMe"href="/champions/shaco">Make your story with Shaco, The Playful Trickster ➤</a>');
                        }

                        typeWriter();
                        setTimeout(endingText, 7000);
                        setTimeout(endingTextTwo, 9000);
                    }
                });
            </script>
